title: Ep - 18 - Daniel Maguire from Bachelor in Paradise
description:
Daniel Maguire from Bachelor in Paradise gives his honest opinion about JoJo and women cast on the show, David Zemon gives his Bachelor fantasy league picks, and Kate quizzes sisters Liz and Teresa about how close their lives resemble that of the Hilton sisters on Real Housewives of Beverly Hills.
